text: Best teh tarik in town!! If you’ve never tried it, you NEED to. Perfect blend that encapsulates the rich creaminess of the tea and perfect amount of sweetness. Originally from Upper Boon Keng market and now located at WIS@Changi. Come down and try it yourself and you’ll fall in love with the teh like many others have

One of the best teh tarik around the area in my opinion.
For 1.30 a cup, it's really a worthy cup of tea. The sweetness is just right, and the portion is large. I would definitely come again for more

A muslim owned teh tarik. Love the quality and the taste of the my Ice Teh Tarek!
Owner is also really friendly and kind.
Smooth, strong and with the right amount of sweetness. My favourite Teh Tarik. The owner was also very friendly
Best teh in Singapore! Small and humble shop but amazing service! So happy they opened up this shop. I’m
